        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Human PSD was isolated from neocortical biopsies of nine adults and subjected to mass-spectrometry analysis. Supplementary Table 12 lists 748 proteins that were detected in all three replicates (\"consensus hPSD\").. Experimental description: \"Biopsies of adults\"" ;
